text: Texas A&M; University–Kingsville is a public university in Kingsville, Texas, United States. It has about 6,500 students enrolled and it was founded in 1925. It has ties to Texas A&M; University. ==References== * ==Other websites== *Texas A&M; University–Kingsville Category:Colleges and universities in Texas Category:1925 establishments in the United States Category:1920s establishments in Texas
